Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Ethics in government
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsy2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 26 Apr 1987
As former White House aide Michael Deaver's trial begins, a look at how widespread is corruption in government. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less